Deploy locally:

1-run anvil
2-copy one of private keys in the .env file like below without double quote and 0x:

PRIVATE_KEY=ac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80

run the following command:

forge script script/Contract.s.sol:ContractScript --fork-url http://localhost:8545 --private-key $PRIVATE_KEY  --broadcast

Deploy on testnet:

1-run anvil
2-copy private key from MetaMask by clicking on "Connection Details" and copy it to .env file like below without double quote and 0x:

PRIVATE_KEY=ac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80

run the following command:

forge script script/Contract.s.sol:ContractScript --rpc-url $ARBITRUM_TESTNET_RPC --private-key ${PRIVATE_KEY} --broadcast
